Gamma calculation engine:\n1. FxVanillaOptionMeasureCalculations (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionMeasureCalculations.java) - wires Black and Vanna-Volga pricers for measures\n2. FxVanillaOptionMethod (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionMethod.java) - enum defining BLACK and VANNA_VOLGA calculation parameters\n3. FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculationFunction (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculationFunction.java) - calculation function implementing CalculationFunction<FxVanillaOptionTrade>\n4. FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculations (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculations.java) - high-level API for calculations on FxVanillaOptionTrade\n\n## Loader Class (modules/loader/)\nFxVanillaOptionTradeCsvPlugin (modules/loader/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/loader/csv/FxVanillaOptionTradeCsvPlugin.java) - implements TradeCsvParserPlugin and TradeCsvWriterPlugin<FxVanillaOptionTrade> for loading/writing CSV files\n\n## Related Class - FxSingleBarrierOption\nFxSingleBarrierOption (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/FxSingleBarrierOption.java) - embeds FxVanillaOption as a dependency (the underlyingOption field). This class represents an FX option with a barrier condition applied to an underlying FxVanillaOption.\n\nNote: The task mentions \"4 pricer classes (Black, Normal, Vanna-Volga, Implied-Tree variants)\" for FxVanillaOption. However, in the actual codebase, there are only Black and Vanna-Volga pricer variants for FxVanillaOption. The ImpliedTrinomialTree (Implied-Tree) pricing methodology is implemented only for FxSingleBarrierOption through ImpliedTrinomialTreeFxSingleBarrierOptionProductPricer and ImpliedTrinomialTreeFxSingleBarrierOptionTradePricer classes."
}

