   132→  "text": "Complete type family for FxVanillaOption in OpenGamma Strata:

## Domain Classes (modules/product/)
The core Joda-Beans domain classes form the foundation of the FxVanillaOption type hierarchy:
1. FxVanillaOption (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/FxVanillaOption.java) - the main domain product class implementing FxOptionProduct and Resolvable<ResolvedFxVanillaOption>
2. FxVanillaOptionTrade (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionTrade.java) - wraps FxVanillaOption with trade metadata, implements ResolvableTrade<ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade>
3. ResolvedFxVanillaOption (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/ResolvedFxVanillaOption.java) - the resolved form with time-bound data, used as input to pricers
4. ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade.java) - resolved trade form implementing ResolvedTrade, the primary input to pricers

## Pricer Classes (modules/pricer/)
For FxVanillaOption, there are two pricing methodologies each with product and trade variants:
1. BlackFxVanillaOptionProductPricer (modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/BlackFxVanillaOptionProductPricer.java) - Black model pricer for products
2. BlackFxVanillaOptionTradePricer (modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/BlackFxVanillaOptionTradePricer.java) - Black model pricer for trades
3. VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionProductPricer (modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionProductPricer.java) - Vanna-Volga model pricer for products
4. VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionTradePricer (modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionTradePricer.java) - Vanna-Volga model pricer for trades

## Measure Classes (modules/measure/)
The calculation framework integrates pricers into the OpenGamma calculation engine:
1. FxVanillaOptionMeasureCalculations (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionMeasureCalculations.java) - wires Black and Vanna-Volga pricers for measures
2. FxVanillaOptionMethod (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionMethod.java) - enum defining BLACK and VANNA_VOLGA calculation parameters
3. FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculationFunction (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculationFunction.java) - calculation function implementing CalculationFunction<FxVanillaOptionTrade>
4. FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculations (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculations.java) - high-level API for calculations on FxVanillaOptionTrade

## Loader Class (modules/loader/)
FxVanillaOptionTradeCsvPlugin (modules/loader/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/loader/csv/FxVanillaOptionTradeCsvPlugin.java) - implements TradeCsvParserPlugin and TradeCsvWriterPlugin<FxVanillaOptionTrade> for loading/writing CSV files

## Related Class - FxSingleBarrierOption
FxSingleBarrierOption (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/FxSingleBarrierOption.java) - embeds FxVanillaOption as a dependency (the underlyingOption field). This class represents an FX option with a barrier condition applied to an underlying FxVanillaOption.

Note: The task mentions "4 pricer classes (Black, Normal, Vanna-Volga, Implied-Tree variants)" for FxVanillaOption. However, in the actual codebase, there are only Black and Vanna-Volga pricer variants for FxVanillaOption. The ImpliedTrinomialTree (Implied-Tree) pricing methodology is implemented only for FxSingleBarrierOption through ImpliedTrinomialTreeFxSingleBarrierOptionProductPricer and ImpliedTrinomialTreeFxSingleBarrierOptionTradePricer classes."
